.DT
remote
Discworld player help
remote

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remote - Echos some text to a specific person.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
remote <person> <text>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Remote takes the text provided and shows it to the person whose name you've
given.  It will appear on their screen with your name prepended to it.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
(If your name is Lynscar)
> remote pinkfish turns you into a frog.

Pinkfish will see:
Lynscar turns you into a frog.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
emote, frimble, lsay, position, say, sayto, soul.
.EP
